text: Shaheed Keshvani (born 23 May 1984) is a Canadian cricketer. He has played five One Day Internationals (ODIs) and two Twenty20 Internationals for Canada. He plays as a middle-order batsman, and bats right-handed. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian cricketers Category:Canada One Day International cricketers Category:Canada Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
